instructions: Place the plate in the centre of the charger.
Place the folded napkin on top of the plate.
Place the dinner fork to the left of the charger with its prongs pointing upwards.
Place the salad fork to the left of the dinner fork with its prongs pointing upwards.
Place the dinner knife to the right of the charger with its blade pointing upwards.
Place the tea spoon to the right of the dinner knife with its bowl facing upwards.
Place the soup spoon to the right of the tea spoon with its bowl pointing upwards.
Place the water glass to the top right side of the charger, above the dinner knife.
Place the wine glass to the right of the water glass, above the tea spoon.
Place another wine glass between the wine glass that was placed previously and the tea spoon.
Place a coffee cup to the top right of the soup spoon.
Place the bread plate to the top left of the charger and above the forks.
Place the butter knife horizontally on the bread plate with its blade pointing to the left.
Place a dessert fork horizontally above the charger with its prongs pointing to the water glass.
Place a dessert spoon horizontally below the dessert fork with its bowl facing the bread plate.
